Project Description
AspNetPager is a free custom paging control for ASP.NET web form application. It's one of the most popular ASP.NET third party controls used by chinese ASP.NET developers.

This project has been moved to: https://github.com/Webdiyer/AspNetPager

Online demo is available at http://en.webdiyer.com/aspnetpager/

Chinese version is available at http://www.webdiyer.com/aspnetpager/
